Questions for interview
-----------------------
Scenario#1
Your manager wants to evaluate employees for promotion. To do this, they need a list of 
all employees ordered by their seniority, starting from the most senior to the most junior.
Write an SQL query to display all employees sorted by their hire date in ascending order. 

Sql:
    SELECT employee_id, name, department, hire_date
    FROM employee
    WHERE hire_date IS NOT NULL
    ORDER BY hire_date ASC;





